subject: resource/Thiruvisaippa
object: Thiruvisaipa (Tamil: திருவிசைப்பா Thiru means "respect", visai means "action" and pa indicates "poem") denotes the ninth volumes of the Tirumurai, the twelve-volume collection of Tamil Saivite devotional poetry.
human_readable: Thiruvisaippa is a volume that denotes the ninth volumes of the Tirumurai, a twelve-volume collection of Tamil Saivite devotional poetry.
